# General

This is the EXT folder. Put any additional library, dependency or plugin
into this folder to have it added to smarti on the next restart of the application.

# plugin-info.json

This files contains JSON formatted information about required plugins.
Typically this is required for GPL licensed modules where the License does not
allow to include them in the installation package.

However this can also be used to distribute huge dependences (e.g. machine learning
models)
